"Neighbor Spoofing is a tactic used by scammers to hide their real caller ID, and instead display a similar number as yours.
This scam is widely used because it’s more likely to answer a number similar to yours. Truecaller enables you to protect yourself against Neighbor Spoofing by blocking numbers starting with the same digits as yours.
You can select to block between 4-6 digits."
